description:
Stunning, spacious, never-lived-in-before corner townhouse in Graduate Hospital. Totaling just over 3,100 sqft, the townhouse comes fully equipped with top of the line finishes and appliances.
The 3-bedroom 4-bathroom home includes both a basement and 2-car garage. A total of 6 levels, the home includes a sprawling balcony off the back of the kitchen as well as a rooftop deck with incredible unobstructed views of Center City.
The 3rd floor consists of two large bedrooms, a bathroom, and a laundry room. The 4th floor is dedicated to the Master Bedroom Suite, with a large bathroom and walk-in closet. The bathroom features an oversized shower and tub, as well as heated tile flooring.
Located just north of Washington Ave, this area is undergoing massive reconstruction and revitalization. Walking distance to Rittenhouse Square, the Schuylkill River, and a ton of great bars and restaurants.
Available mid- to end-July. This won't last! Contact us for further information.
